game.name: Highway Traffic Bike Stunts
game.description:
It is time to prove your biking skills and perform some death-defying stunts on your own! Are you ready to take on this challenge and prove the world that you are a real biker? If yes, Highway Traffic Bike Stunts game is a nice bet for you. In this one of the best bike racing games for boys, your objective is to ride a wonderful sports bike on the crazy asphalt racing tracks. The maximum number of stunts you perform the higher score you will be able to make.

You would like to go through all the levels of this highly addictive online game if you are a true fan of stunt bike simulation skills. So why do you need to wait anymore? Take your seat on your chosen motorcycle and gear up to perform as many stunts as you can while having the maximum number of near misses to score high! Track your speed by having a look at the top right corner of the screen in this HTML5 bike driving simulator!

Common friends! The world of best superbike stunt racing is waiting for you. All you need to do is maintain the balance of your bike and make sure to build the ramps if needed to jump train platform or any other obstacles. Get your bike and head on to ride the extremely crazy asphalt racing tracks in the mid of the city highway traffic rush! Many other top racing titles are available on atmegame.com to keep you engrossed for hours. Good luck!
